OL,3,CMan defrauded elderly mum of more than
OL,4,C#100,000 to pay own bills
OL,6,FAt the same time, he failed to visit
OL,7,Fhis mother in the care home, West
OL,8,FYorkshire Trading Standards said.
OL,10,FHe failed to provide toiletries and
OL,11,Fother items that she needed, leaving
OL,12,Fthe care home having to rely on
OL,13,Fdonations provide her essentials.
OL,15,FCatlow was investigated by Trading
OL,16,FStandards on behalf of Calderdale
OL,17,FCouncil after concerns were raised in
OL,18,FMay 2021.
