OL,3,CMan defrauded elderly mum of more than
OL,4,C#100,000 to pay own bills
OL,6,FHe eventually admitted fraud by abuse
OL,7,Fof position and was given a two-year
OL,8,Fsuspended prison sentence.
OL,10,FLinda Davis, head of the West
OL,11,FYorkshire financial exploitation and
OL,12,Fabuse team said: "Robert Catlow was in
OL,13,Fa significant position of trust, and
OL,14,Fhe abused that position, using his
OL,15,Fmother's money to finance his own
OL,16,Flifestyle and business and leaving her
OL,17,Fwithout money for anything such as
OL,18,Fpersonal care items.
